Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 @cher喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說了不是啦！
